ADDITIONAL INFORMATION FOR APP STORE CONNECT:

Data Collection Practices:
- The App collects location data when users actively use the GPS tracking feature
- All data is stored locally on the user's device
- No data is transmitted to external servers
- No data is shared with third parties
- Users can delete data by uninstalling the App

Data Used to Track You:
- None. The App does not track users across other apps or websites.

Data Linked to You:
- Location data (only when using GPS tracking)
- Running activity data (stored locally only)

Data Not Linked to You:
- None collected

Data Not Collected:
- Personal identification information (name, email, phone number)
- Payment information
- Contact information
- Device identifiers for tracking
- Advertising identifiers

